Aqoin is an online wallet, a payment processing system for Bitcoin and a [[currency_exchange]] site serving those trading between bitcoins and the following currencies:

* EUR (Euro)

The languages supported by the site are Spanish and English.

The service was announced September 1th, 2011.

##Adding Funds

###EUR (Bank transfer)
Funds may be added using SEPA zone bank wires or International wire transfers.  Those in Spain can select the national (domestic) wire transfer method.

##Withdrawing Funds

###EUR (Bank transfer)
Funds may be withdrawn as SEPA zone bank wires or those in Spain can select the national (domestic) wire transfer method.

###PayPal
Funds may be withdrawn to PayPal.

##Aqoin payments module
The aqoin payments module allows online merchants to offer their products and services in Bitcoins. It allows instant payments using aqoin accounts or payments throught Bitcoin network.

